Fluid-trac
----------
Website: http://www.ssitechnologies.com/fluidtrac.html

Only seems to work up to 24" in gasoline. Not going to work well
for our 27" tank.

Price around $100

Fuel Minder
-----------
Website: http://www.sybasystems.com/Fuel%20Minder/fuel_minder_remote_gauge.html

Is a little expensive since it comes with a gauge. It uses a cork for
floatation device. Is it really precise enough?

Price: $150



